<leg:heading><desig searchtype="PART-NUM"><designum><refpt id="UCPN.OL.CLAN02.PT6" type="ext"/>PART 6</designum></desig><title searchtype="PART-TITLE">INTOXICATION [ss 47&#x2013;50]</title><leg:histnote>
<p><text>[Pt 6  insrt  Act 92 of 2002   sÂ 3 and Sch 1, effective 6 December 2002]</text></p></leg:histnote></leg:heading>
